title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 71 - The Evolution of Titties (ft. Joey Camasta)
description:
Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 71 - The Evolution of Titties (ft. Joey Camasta) -- The boys are back in the radio room to discuss their weekends, Andrew Tate, murder bloggers, stand-up, pup punk, the Most Dangerous Gameshow, Marilyn Monroe stinking to high heavens, & the evolution of titties, as well as a pop-in/Jersey Shore recap from Out and About's Joey Camasta -- Enjoy!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
